reviewText:
OMG what a tedious couple of hours of my life that I shall never get back. I gave it to an acquaintance as I would never take the chance of loosing a close friend by insulting their intellegence. The acting (if one could be so bold as to call it that) was dreadful, uninspiring and really boring I would prefer to shoot myself in the foot rather than be tortured by watching this again.
What a load of rot.
